data.title: Future Judicial Vacancies
data.meta_description: This table lists judicial vacancies that will occur in the future, for instance if a current federal judge announces their retirement. Find out the court where the vacancy will occur, the name of the incumbent, the vacancy reason, the vacancy notification date, the vacancy date, and the nominee and nomination date, if applicable.
